OL,3,CPolice officer appears in court over
OL,4,Ccollision between police car and e-bike
OL,6,FA police officer has appeared in court
OL,7,Fcharged with causing serious injury by
OL,8,Fdangerous driving in connection with a
OL,9,Fcollision between his police car and
OL,10,Fan electric bike.
OL,12,FPc Tim Bradshaw attended Portsmouth
OL,13,FMagistrates' Court to face the charge
OL,14,Frelating to the incident in Hawthorn
OL,15,FRoad, Bognor Regis, West Sussex, on
OL,16,FNovember 3 2022.
