OL,3,CPolice officer appears in court over
OL,4,Ccollision between police car and e-bike
OL,6,FThe court heard that the rider of the
OL,7,Felectric bike suffered a fractured
OL,8,Fknee and a broken thighbone in the
OL,9,Fcollision which happened as Bradshaw
OL,10,Fwas allegedly attempting to stop the
OL,11,Fbike.
OL,13,FThe case was adjourned to be heard at
OL,14,FPortsmouth Crown Court on May 7 and
OL,15,FBradshaw, who serves with Sussex
OL,16,FPolice, was released on bail until
OL,17,Fthen.
