OL,6,FSussex Police said in a statement
OL,7,Freleased after Bradshaw was charged:
OL,8,F"The matter was referred to the
OL,9,FIndependent Office of Police Conduct
OL,10,Fwho directed that a local
OL,11,Finvestigation by Sussex Police should
OL,12,Fbe conducted.
OL,14,F"The force will consider misconduct
OL,15,Fproceedings once the criminal
OL,16,Fproceedings have concluded."
